  "detailed_description": "<h1>Update</h1><p>1.Delete Bulge&Pit and Paint&Decal functions.\r\n2.Change the leviathan  model.\r\n3.Add 10 kinds of color leviathans.\r\n4.Add leviathan hunter spaceship.\r\nLeviathan hunter spaceship control:\r\nmove forward:key W\r\nmove back:key S\r\nturn left:key A\r\nturn right:key D\r\nshoot: key Space</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Leviathan is third person view  control whale phagocytosis game.\r\nSupport to bulge&pit the Leviathan mesh and paint color&decal the Leviathan material.\r\nAct as a Leviathan,move the Leviathan to hit the samller Leviathan to get score, avoid the bigger Leviathan.\r\nControl:\r\n1.Bulge&Pit scene.long click mouse left button to bulge mesh,long click mouse right button to pit mesh.\r\n2.Paint&Decal scene.first, click Paint/Decal button,then press mouse left button to Paint/Decal mesh.\r\n3.Play scene.press mouse right button to rotate Leviathan.\r\nmove forward:key W\r\nmove back:key S\r\nturn left:key A\r\nturn right:key D",
  "about_the_game": "Leviathan is third person view  control whale phagocytosis game.<br />\r\nSupport to bulge&pit the Leviathan mesh and paint color&decal the Leviathan material.<br />\r\nAct as a Leviathan,move the Leviathan to hit the samller Leviathan to get score, avoid the bigger Leviathan.<br />\r\nControl:<br />\r\n1.Bulge&Pit scene.long click mouse left button to bulge mesh,long click mouse right button to pit mesh.<br />\r\n2.Paint&Decal scene.first, click Paint/Decal button,then press mouse left button to Paint/Decal mesh.<br />\r\n3.Play scene.press mouse right button to rotate Leviathan.<br />\r\nmove forward:key W<br />\r\nmove back:key S<br />\r\nturn left:key A<br />\r\nturn right:key D",
